---
title: Red Pepper Chilli Jelly Glazed Double Sausage Bake with Sweet Potato Wedges, Zingy Baby Gem and Peanut Salad
description: It only takes 10 minutes to prep this Red Pepper Chilli Jelly Glazed Double Sausage Bake. Everything goes straight into the oven whilst you make the salad for an easy dinner that gives you time back!
